‚Çπ2500 daily - 20 members



Total Value: ‚Çπ5,00,000

After Lifting: ‚Çπ3000 daily





Custom Scheme

Create your own scheme



Flexible parameters

Custom rules





      {/* Create/Edit Form Modal */}
      {showCreateForm && (






